/*************************************************************
* Replace RCInputs jQuery plugin
* 
* Created & copyright (c) by Mike Behnke
*
* http://www.local-pc-guy.com
* Twitter: @LocalPCGuy
*
* Description: Basic plugin to create a graphic to use in 
* place of a checkbox or radio button.  Styles for the 
* checked/non-checked state should be defined in a 
* stylesheet, and the plugin mearly changes the class and 
* keeps the checkbox updated.
*
* usage:
*        $("input[name=rDemo]").replaceRCInputs({hideInputs: false});
*        $("#checkboxDemo").replaceRCInputs({hideInputs: false});
*
* options: 
	{
		toggleClass: "toggle",
		checkedClass: "checked",
		hideInputs: true
	}
*
* https://github.com/localpcguy/replaceRCInputs
* Released under MIT License
* http://lpg.mit-license.org/
*
*************************************************************/